    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The thick, resinous exudation from the species Pinus pinaster of southern Europe, especially France. Galipot is similar to Venice turpentine (a balsam) and can be distilled to produce oil of turpentine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
